{
  "id": "adv_event_2311_01_02",
  "title": "負ける訳には\nいかない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "— A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 0.9999999881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "次の対戦相手が正式に決定したわ\nライブに向けてさらに気合いを入れていくわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The next opponent has been officially decided.\nWe’re going to put even more effort into the live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.7999999523,
      "endTime": 8.2199998378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "と言っても、VENUSプログラムのスコアでは\nトリエルの方が安定して高得点を出してるんよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ looking at the VENUS program scores‚\nTRINITYAiLE has been getting consistently high scores.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4133332093,
      "endTime": 15.4187074502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "普段通りの実力を発揮出来れば\nうちらなら勝てるはずや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we can perform at our usual level‚\nwe should be able to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6253742695,
      "endTime": 20.398866415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、特別なことは何もしないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So we’re not going to do anything special?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.598866415,
      "endTime": 24.433968544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。いつも通り歌い慣れた曲で\nより完成度を高めることを目指しましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. We’re going to aim\nto improve the perfection of our performance as usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6206350963,
      "endTime": 30.7090705554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "いつもやってることをいつも通りに……\n結局それが一番確実で、勝率が高い方法やもんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doing what we always do‚ the way we always do it…\nIn the end‚ that’s the most reliable and surest way to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.90907046,
      "endTime": 39.548639551799994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "勝率か……。うん、そうだね\nじゃあいつも通りに頑張ろー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The winning percentage huh… Yeah‚ you’re right.\nAlright‚ let’s do our best as usual!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7486396472,
      "endTime": 47.3153327624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "（どうしてかな？　また胸がざわざわして……）\n（この感じ、一体なんなんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I wonder why? My chest feels uneasy again…)\n(What is this feeling?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5019994576,
      "endTime": 56.234992392799995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブバトル当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "— On the day of the live battle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2483255545,
      "endTime": 58.7816575925,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1733.3321094999974
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.881657664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "今日は沢山の声援をありがとうございました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much for all your support today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.814990441,
      "endTime": 63.5149905364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.7083238125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんの応援のおかげで\n99連勝を達成することが出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to your support‚\nwe were able to achieve 99th straight win!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7083238125,
      "endTime": 69.2887321949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.4953989188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ100連勝に王手や\nうちらの次のライブバトルも期待してて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re finally one step away from 100th straight win.\nPlease look forward to our next live battle!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4953989188,
      "endTime": 75.8924510161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.0991174538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "私達はこれからも勝ち続けます！\nTRINITYAiLEはどこまでも飛び続けます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll keep winning!\nTRINITYAiLE will keep soaring to new heights!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0991174538,
      "endTime": 82.4646277269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.6712943554
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（格の違いを見せつけて完全勝利か、さすがだな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(A complete victory‚ showing the difference in class. They’re amazing…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6712943554,
      "endTime": 87.6560563564,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.8560563564
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（人気、実力、共に充実している今のトリエルなら）\n（次のステップに進んでも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(With their current popularity and skills‚ TRINITYAiLE)\n(could take the next step…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8560563564,
      "endTime": 94.7560562611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.2446706139
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.6113372806
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.0127228896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！　100戦目の対戦相手にVENUSプログラム\nランキング五位のアイドルを！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?! A top 5 idol in the VENUS program rankings\nfor our 100th opponent?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0627228896,
      "endTime": 103.87177039779999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。今までの相手とは比べものにならない強敵だが\n今のトリエルなら十分勝ち目はあると俺は思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. They’re a formidable opponent‚ unlike any we’ve faced before‚\nbut I believe the current TRINITYAiLE has a good chance of winning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.0717704932,
      "endTime": 111.6315208594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "もし、それでうちらがランキング五位に勝ったら\nその次は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we manage to defeat a top 5 ranked idol‚\nthen next…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8181871414,
      "endTime": 116.9581877548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.8181876023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよBIG4に挑戦だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll finally challenge the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.171521012,
      "endTime": 119.6315210978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.8181876976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "私達がBIG4に……サニピに挑戦出来る……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We… can challenge the BIG4… Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8181876976,
      "endTime": 125.13728073429999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.3306140105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYでのゴタゴタに巻き込まれたせいで\nトリエルは実力はあるのにチャンスに恵まれなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because you were caught up in the I-UNITY mess‚\nTRINITYAiLE didn’t get the chance we deserved despite their skills.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3306140105,
      "endTime": 131.32122632660003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だが、100連勝がかかった今なら\nたとえトップ5でもトリエルの挑戦を断れないはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ with 100 consecutive wins at stake‚\neven the top 5 won’t be able to refuse TRINITYAiLE’s challenge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.5078930695,
      "endTime": 137.9757163843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.1757164796
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "上位ランカーに挑戦するまたとないチャンス\nいうことやな。どないする、瑠依ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to challenge\na high-ranking idol. What do you say‚ Rui-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1757164796,
      "endTime": 145.84703148190002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.0603646437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん\n三人で相談してもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
